title: Lindsay Kimball, Program Director at The Current, reflects music connecting people and membership.

description:
The Current host Mac Wilson talks about how The Current builds connections among people through the power of music. The Current has been an invaluable resource to the music community since it launched in 2005 and it’s all because of you, our incredible community of artists, listeners and members. Thank you.
